1
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,640
(Episode 22)

2
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,720
I don't want to be stuck in this hospital.

3
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,720
It's like a cage in here.

4
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:39,760
Sister Xiaomeng.

5
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:42,640
Can you take me home?

6
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:46,400
Tiankong, what's wrong with this place?

7
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,400
Look.

8
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,160
All these big sisters are here
to play with you.

9
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,440
And a big brother too.

10
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,680
No. It's not nice at all.

11
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,760
I don't want injections,
I don't want pills,

12
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,400
and I don't want surgery!

13
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,800
Sister Xiaomeng.

14
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:01,240
I'll behave.

15
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:04,960
Please don't send me here again.

16
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,640
I hate this place!

17
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:09,120
Alright, Tiankong. Don't cry.

18
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:11,720
Why don't I take you out to play?

19
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:15,160
Tiankong,
I know a place that's really fun.

20
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,400
Do you want to go there?

21
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:18,600
You're not lying, right?

22
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,760
Where is this place?

23
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,360
Come, let's find out.

24
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,320
Let me help you get changed.

25
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,360
Here, put these on.

26
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,760
These will protect your eyes
when you go out.

27
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:40,080
Sister Xiaomeng, are we in a park?

28
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,880
How did you know?

29
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:44,160
I can smell it, and hear it.

30
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:47,000
I can smell the grass, and the flowers.

31
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:49,440
There are many trees and birds here.

32
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,360
You're so smart, Tiankong.

33
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,040
You're completely right.

34
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:57,520
Sister Xiaomeng, why did you take me here?

35
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:02,280
Because you're the most well-behaved
and the bravest boy ever.

36
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,720
Over the next few days,

37
00:03:03,840 --> 00:03:07,800
Sister Qiao Zhen, Brother Xiao, and I

38
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,440
will all play with you.

39
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,320
-Alright?
-Yes!

40
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,480
Tiankong!

41
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,720
Tiankong!

42
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,040
Are you okay?

43
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,040
Sister Xiaomeng.

44
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,480
Are you doing this

45
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:24,680
because I'm about to do my surgery?

46
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,520
Sister Xiaomeng,

47
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:33,920
I know you're doing this just for me.

48
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,400
But I'm really scared.

49
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,960
I don't want to undergo surgery.

50
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,080
I heard some people couldn't see

51
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:41,200
after they did their surgery.

52
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:44,440
Sister Xiaomeng,
talk to the doctor for me.

53
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:47,280
Tell him not to do the surgery, please?

54
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,800
Tiankong.
Let's not think about anything today.

55
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,720
Let's just play and have fun, okay?

56
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,680
Yes, let's play together.

57
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,640
You're flying!

58
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,120
Is this fun?

59
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,320
Yes!

60
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:13,480
Tiankong, don't you feel
like a bird flying?

61
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,800
Very much!

62
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,240
Let's fly!

63
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:22,720
Let's fly!

64
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,600
Little bird fly!

65
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,040
I'm flying!

66
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,360
Tiankong.

67
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,120
What are you thinking
in that little head of yours?

68
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:42,320
I was thinking if only I was a bird.

69
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:45,400
I could fly to wherever I want to go.

70
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,360
Tiankong, you know?

71
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:50,960
I want to be a bird too.

72
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,520
I want to fly freely

73
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,560
in the sky.

74
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,560
Sister Xiaomeng, let's fly together.

75
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,800
We'll fly across the sea

76
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,440
all the way to the clouds, okay?

77
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:04,040
Yes. I will go with you.

78
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:06,880
Let's fly! Fly!

79
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:11,040
Brother, can I really be a bird?

80
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,920
Of course you can be a bird.

81
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,560
You can fly in the sky,

82
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,160
and touch the clouds.

83
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,520
When you look down from the sky,

84
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,200
you'll see the green grass,

85
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,400
the red flowers,

86
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,960
and the sparkling rivers.

87
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:26,640
But I'm about to lose my eyesight.

88
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:33,800
Tiankong,

89
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:36,440
do you want to see this beautiful world?

90
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,240
Yes. But I don't want to do surgery.

91
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,600
Do you know what I do?

92
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,800
I know. You're a doctor.

93
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,480
I am a doctor.

94
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,000
That's why I can promise you,

95
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,560
after your surgery,

96
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,200
you'll recover very quickly.

97
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:54,720
Will I be able to see everything
after my surgery?

98
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,480
I promise you.

99
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,760
Look at this flower.

100
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,560
After your surgery,

101
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,160
you will see

102
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:10,040
its red petals and green leaves.

103
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,360
Tiankong,

104
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,760
what do you want to be when you grow up?

105
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,040
I want to be a painter!

106
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:18,240
But if I can't see anything,

107
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:20,520
I won't be able to paint anymore.

108
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,760
Tiankong, I have faith in you.

109
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,720
When your eyes get better,

110
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,640
you'll definitely be able to paint again.

111
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:31,800
You'll paint such a colorful world.

112
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,360
But I'm afraid of the pain.

113
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:35,840
People say surgeries are painful.

114
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,320
Remember what Sister Xiaomeng said?

115
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,360
You're the bravest boy

116
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:41,800
in the world.

117
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,440
If only it wouldn't hurt at all.

118
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,480
I'm a doctor.

119
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,560
I know this surgery well.

120
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:51,400
It'll be like going to sleep.

121
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,600
When you wake up and open your eyes,

122
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,520
you'll be able to see Sister Xiaomeng

123
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,600
and Director Lin clearly.

124
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:59,040
Really? Will it not hurt at all?

125
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,040
Of course!

126
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,040
He's a doctor. He's always right.

127
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:05,640
We'll be with you the whole time.

128
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,360
We'll be rooting for you.

129
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:10,160
Sister Xiaomeng. Will you be with me

130
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,880
during the surgery too?

131
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,520
Of course, Tiankong.

132
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,120
I promise you.

133
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:18,240
All of us will be with you.

134
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,040
After your surgery,

135
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,880
you'll be able to see all of us

136
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,760
and continue painting.

137
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:26,200
You'll be a painter again.

138
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,320
Sister Xiaomeng. I'll do as you say.

139
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,760
I'll do the surgery.

140
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,920
After the surgery,

141
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,200
I'll be able to see you,

142
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:34,720
Sister Qiao Zhen, and Big Brother.

143
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,200
Oh right, and Mommy Lin too.

144
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,320
Also, I want to continue painting.

145
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,480
Tiankong, you're the best.

146
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,680
Good job, we're so proud of you.

147
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,480
Thank you, Sister Xiaomeng.

148
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,920
Thank you, Sister Qiao Zhen.

149
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,240
Thank you, Big Brother.

150
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,160
Tiankong,

151
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:51,080
the person you should thank the most

152
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,760
is Big Brother.

153
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,360
When my eyes get better,

154
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:56,480
I'll make a drawing of you.

155
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,720
Make sure you make him look handsome.

156
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:03,320
He's so ugly.

157
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,680
Big Brother, are you ugly?

158
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,840
I'll make you better looking.

159
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:11,040
Don't get mad. Here.

160
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,880
Have some fruit. You'll look better.

161
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,480
I'm not angry.

162
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,200
You're right.

163
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,440
Tiankong.

164
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,720
Let's eat fruit too.

165
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,320
Are you ticklish? Are you?

166
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,360
Are you ticklish?

167
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:44,800
Dr. Xiao, Senior.

168
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:47,880
Thank you guys for staying with

169
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,640
Tiankong and I these last few days.

170
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,240
Thank you so much.

171
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:53,840
No worries.

172
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:55,360
We had a lot of fun too.

173
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:57,240
I haven't had so much fun in a while.

174
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,800
You were with Tiankong all day today.

175
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:02,800
You haven't eaten anything at all.

176
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:06,560
How about I'll treat you dinner later?

177
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:09,440
Xiaomeng, I'm a doctor.

178
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,520
It's my job.

179
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:13,400
Take Qiao Zhen out,

180
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:14,560
I'll stay

181
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,160
That's so impolite.

182
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,600
Xiaomeng wants to treat us.

183
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,920
How could you turn her down?

184
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:29,080
Exactly. Both of you have to come.

185
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,480
Alright then.

186
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:32,800
But I don't think
it's right for you to pay.

187
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,040
I'll pay instead.

188
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,400
Sure.

189
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:39,320
Xiaomeng will take us out.
Dr. Xiao will pay for it.

190
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,480
Perfect.

191
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,080
That'll make me happy.

192
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,920
Sister Xiaomeng, where are you guys going?

193
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,400
I want to come too.

194
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,640
Tiankong, not tonight.

195
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,240
It's getting late.

196
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,440
You should go to bed soon.

197
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:55,200
Alright, I'll take Tiankong to his ward.

198
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,720
You guys wait for me in the restaurant.

199
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:59,680
But I want to be with Sister Xiaomeng
a little longer.

200
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,880
Sister Xiaomeng, take me back to the ward.

201
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,320
-Okay, okay.
-Be good.

202
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,920
Tiankong.

203
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,160
You must listen to me.

204
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,160
How about this?

205
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,480
I'll take Tiankong back,

206
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,480
you guys can go ahead.

207
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,600
I'll join you later.

208
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,360
That sounds good.

209
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:20,800
Dr. Xiao, let's go.

210
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,880
But...

211
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,600
No buts.

212
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:27,280
He'll be safer with Xiaomeng
than any doctor.

213
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,760
Come on, let's go.

214
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,080
Don't worry. Let's go.

215
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,200
Xiaomeng, hurry up!

216
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:37,440
Alright, I will.

217
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,240
Let's go.

218
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:44,960
Tiankong, let's go back.

219
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:51,720
Dr. Xiao, you don't mind
paying for our dinner?

220
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,160
Of course not.

221
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:56,240
You wouldn't mind paying
for Xiaomeng of course.

222
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,480
But now there's just the two of us.

223
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,480
I don't know if you'll mind.

224
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,400
What are you talking about?

225
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:08,160
Alright then. It's a deal.

226
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,400
I'm going to order
the most expensive stuff.

227
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,880
I'll order the entire menu.

228
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:21,840
Qiao Zhen. Actually a doctor

229
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,800
doesn't make nearly as much
as people say we do.

230
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,880
Go easy on me.

231
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:30,640
You're so cute.

232
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,520
Come on, let's go.

233
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,600
Sister Xiaomeng,

234
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:41,400
why don't you tell me your favorite story?

235
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:44,840
Alright, I'll tell you a story

236
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:47,640
about a playground, okay?

237
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:48,920
Yes!

238
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,520
I want to go to a playground.

239
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:54,320
There was a girl named Wendy.

240
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,360
She really, really liked playgrounds.

241
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:59,440
Her brother Jack adored her.

242
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:00,680
And so,

243
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:03,520
Jack built a mini playground for Wendy

244
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,440
in their own house.

245
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:07,520
There were many

246
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:10,400
cute little things in that playground.

247
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:13,720
Such as a little train filled with eggs.

248
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:19,240
At night, all these toys

249
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,480
all came alive.

250
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,880
(A Yan)

251
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,440
I'm busy. What is it?

252
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,960
Well,

253
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,720
Tiankong's surgery is tomorrow.

254
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,480
I want to stay

255
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,760
at the hospital with him tonight.
Is that okay?

256
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,640
A Yan?

257
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,800
Alright, sure.

258
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,080
Go ahead.

259
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,640
But...

260
00:13:11,160 --> 00:13:13,080
I'm a little worried about my mom.

261
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:15,320
She's alone at home.

262
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:19,000
I'll get Guang and Sister Hua
to take care of her.

263
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,480
-You...
-Yes?

264
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:24,760
Be safe.

265
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,760
Okay, I will.

266
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:53,120
Take a break and have a coffee.

267
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,440
I'm almost done. Thank you.

268
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,320
You're welcome.

269
00:13:58,920 --> 00:13:59,800
Um...

270
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:03,160
there's a new Japanese restaurant

271
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:06,840
on Xingfu Street that's very authentic.

272
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:07,800
I was thinking...

273
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:09,640
Qingyan.

274
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,200
President Zhou.

275
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,960
Thanks for your hard work.

276
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:25,080
Once you're done with the documents,
go home and get some rest.

277
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:27,200
Tomorrow will be another tough battle.

278
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:30,360
With you around,
we're not afraid of any battles.

