00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:12,240
I want to toast you

563
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:15,520
for saving Tiankong.

564
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,480
You saved his life

565
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,680
and you saved our home.

566
00:34:20,040 --> 00:34:20,840
Director Lin.

567
00:34:21,120 --> 00:34:22,360
Please don't say that.

568
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:25,520
I grew up on welfare myself.

569
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,840
It made me what I am.

570
00:34:27,160 --> 00:34:28,520
You're so modest.

571
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:31,720
This toast is on behalf of Tiankong,

572
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:35,800
but I also want to congratulate
you and Qiao Zhen.

573
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:39,480
I just heard about it.
You're such a good match.

574
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:42,000
I wish you all the best.

575
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:44,280
Thanks Director Lin.

576
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:46,360
Dr. Xiao and I

577
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:48,480
will come by the home a lot more often.

578
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,720
You must.

579
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:52,160
Let's make a toast to Director Lin.

580
00:34:52,200 --> 00:34:53,120
Okay.

581
00:34:53,160 --> 00:34:54,560
Why are you toasting me?

582
00:34:54,680 --> 00:34:56,000
I'm the oldest here.

583
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:04,720
Xiaomeng,

584
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:08,520
Qiao Zhen and Dr. Xiao,

585
00:35:09,600 --> 00:35:11,840
you three are so kind.

586
00:35:12,680 --> 00:35:15,040
I'm so lucky to have met

587
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,920
the three of you.

588
00:35:19,160 --> 00:35:22,240
If only there are more people like you,

589
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:25,200
this world would be so much better.

590
00:35:25,720 --> 00:35:26,560
Director Lin,

591
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:29,080
stop flattering us three.

592
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:31,400
It's making me dizzy.

593
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:33,280
Come, let's eat.

594
00:35:33,600 --> 00:35:34,960
-Let's eat.
-Why are you looking at me?

595
00:35:35,000 --> 00:35:36,720
Let's stop talking and eat.

596
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:39,360
Senior, let's drink another glass.

597
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:40,960
Okay.

598
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:42,680
Cheers to all of us.

599
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:45,640
-Sure.
-Here's to happiness.

600
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:47,000
-Here's to happiness.
-Okay.

601
00:35:47,040 --> 00:35:48,760
-Here's to happiness.
-Here's to happiness.

602
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:56,080
This restaurant is so good.

603
00:35:56,680 --> 00:35:57,600
Yes, it is.

604
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:00,920
How are we leaving?

605
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,360
Senior,

606
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:03,520
you've been so busy the last two days.

607
00:36:03,640 --> 00:36:04,520
You must be tired.

608
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:06,080
You don't have to come
to the hospital tomorrow.

609
00:36:06,240 --> 00:36:08,040
I can take care of Tiankong myself.

610
00:36:08,600 --> 00:36:10,800
It's been really busy at the station.

611
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:12,720
I really should get back to work.

612
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:15,360
Xiaomeng, where are you parked at?

613
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:17,600
In the parking lot behind.

614
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,000
I'm parked there too.

615
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:21,040
Director Lin, Qiao Zhen,

616
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,600
-I'll get the car.
-Wait here.

617
00:36:22,640 --> 00:36:23,560
-Go ahead.
-Okay.

618
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:25,040
-Go.
-Bye.

619
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:29,400
Dr. Xiao, I never thought

620
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:31,440
you and Senior

621
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:33,400
would get together so quickly.

622
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:36,400
I already knew Senior likes you.

623
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:38,320
But you were always so slow.

624
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:41,200
I tried to give you hints so many times.

625
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:43,960
I'm such a dummy.

626
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:45,920
But I knew how she felt.

627
00:36:46,240 --> 00:36:48,800
I was just too cowardly
when it came to love.

628
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,520
I must thank Qiao Zhen.

629
00:36:51,560 --> 00:36:52,920
She gave me the courage

630
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,720
to make the leap.

631
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:59,320
Look how far we've come.

632
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,680
We did the art show,

633
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,360
and you and Senior got together.

634
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:06,360
Tiankong will be able to see too.

635
00:37:07,160 --> 00:37:08,880
So many happy things have happened.

636
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:10,000
How wonderful!

637
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:15,480
What's wrong?

638
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,680
Xiaomeng.

639
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:23,760
Something has been weighing on me.

640
00:37:25,120 --> 00:37:26,120
What is it?

641
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:30,720
The person who actually
helped Tiankong wasn't me.

642
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,600
You've told me before.

643
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:36,080
It was Jiang Ze who helped.

644
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,400
He got in touch with
the specialist from overseas.

645
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:42,160
I'll buy you all dinner soon.

646
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:43,880
It wasn't him.

647
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,800
It wasn't Jiang Ze?

648
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:50,320
Then why did he say yes when I told him

649
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:51,880
I wanted to thank him?

650
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,880
I don't know.

651
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:56,080
He probably doesn't want to miss

652
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:57,720
a chance to have dinner with you.

653
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:00,640
If it wasn't Jiang Ze,

654
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,720
then who was it

655
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:05,120
who helped so much?

656
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:10,400
It was the boss of Shenghai Group.

657
00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:16,080
You mean A Yan?

658
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:19,080
Xiaomeng,

659
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:20,920
I'm just an average doctor.

660
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:24,800
I don't have the power to get
Tiankong a cornea donor.

661
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:27,240
Many people wanted to help Tiankong.

662
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:30,160
But the person who helped the most
was Mr. Zhou.

663
00:38:30,640 --> 00:38:33,240
He was the one
who got in touch with cornea centers

664
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,680
and cornea donor organizations.

665
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:37,840
He found a donor organization in Sri Lanka

666
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,400
who agreed to give Tiankong a cornea.

667
00:38:40,200 --> 00:38:42,200
I was shocked too when I found out.

668
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:43,920
But that's the truth.

669
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:47,240
The person we should thank the most
is Zhou Yanzhao.

670
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,680
Then why didn't you tell me earlier?

671
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,760
He didn't want me to.

672
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:56,320
I think he has his own plans.

673
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,400
Xiaomeng,

674
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,520
you should sit down with him

675
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:03,200
and clear your misunderstandings.

676
00:39:06,960 --> 00:39:08,040
I don't know

677
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:10,960
if I'll ever get the chance to do that.

678
00:39:14,840 --> 00:39:16,080
(Qiao Zhen)

679
00:39:16,240 --> 00:39:18,000
Qiao Zhen's calling. Let's go.

680
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:31,200
-See you then.
-Okay.

681
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:32,360
Your car's here.

682
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:37,520
Director Lin, let me take you.

683
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:38,440
Thank you.

684
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:46,280
Be safe. See you.

685
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:02,720
Director Lin,

686
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:05,640
Tiankong will be able to see again
in a few days.

687
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:09,320
I'll come to the hospital
to see him often.

688
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:10,680
So don't worry.

689
00:40:11,720 --> 00:40:14,280
I really don't know
how to thank you, Xiaomeng.

690
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:16,200
You didn't have to do so much.

691
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:18,040
You've done so much

692
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:20,320
so that Tiankong can see.

693
00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:22,320
If it hadn't been for you,

694
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:24,000
I don't know what would've happened.

695
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:27,200
It was fate for me to meet Tiankong.

696
00:40:27,680 --> 00:40:29,360
When I was feeling down,

697
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:31,600
he also helped me a lot.

698
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:34,280
That's why, Tiankong is lucky

699
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,680
to have a sister like you.

700
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,480
You're his mother now.

701
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:40,600
He's really lucky to have you.

702
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:42,160
Yes.

703
00:40:45,760 --> 00:40:49,920
But this surgery was very high risk.

704
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:53,320
I kept reassuring Tiankong,

705
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:54,600
but deep inside

706
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:56,200
I was still worried.

707
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:57,960
I'm sure

708
00:40:58,640 --> 00:41:00,600
it was the ring you gave Tiankong

709
00:41:00,960 --> 00:41:02,560
before the surgery

710
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:03,920
that brought him good luck.

711
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:39,920
Tiankong.

712
00:41:40,160 --> 00:41:41,840
This is my protective charm.

713
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,520
My mother left this for me.

714
00:41:45,520 --> 00:41:46,880
Now I'm giving it to you.

715
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:01,760
Director Lin.

716
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,800
This is Zhou Yanzhao from Shenghai Group.

717
00:42:06,200 --> 00:42:08,760
Mr. Zhou, nice to meet you.

718
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:17,400
I had a child

719
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:20,080
when I was younger.

720
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:24,120
But I lost him after all.

721
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,080
(Facial recognition system processing...)

722
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:31,280
(Complete)

723
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:34,120
(Test Results)

724
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:37,720
How...

725
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,960
How could this be?

726
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:44,680
(97% maternity match suggested)

727
00:42:47,720 --> 00:42:49,080
That means...

728
00:42:50,920 --> 00:42:52,320
Uncle Zhou...

729
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:56,120
really wasn't A Yan's father?
